                            <comment id="14001451" author="matei" created="Mon, 19 May 2014 07:25:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;BTW the warning on Java 8 is the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM warning: ignoring option MaxPermSize=128m; support was removed in 8.0
&lt;/pre&gt;
